metadata.name: cone and the city_SIN_2018
metadata.description: The cone and the city photo series is a "landscape with road cones" that Yoshihiro Taniguchi has been photographing since 2010. All photographs were taken with an iphone, no zooming or cropping was done during the shooting. The road cones were not moved or modified in any way during the shooting. The locations of the photographs were taken in Osaka, Tokyo, all over Japan, Asia, United States, Europe, and other wide areas.
